<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.7.7">
<l>muṉaitta cīṟṟam viṇcuṭappōy mūvula kumpiṟavum</l>
<l>aṉaittu mañca vāḷariyā yiruntavam māṉatiṭam</l>
<l>kaṉaitta tīyuṅ kallumallā villuṭai vēṭarumāy</l>
<l>tiṉaitta ṉaiyuñ cellavoṇṇāc ciṅkavēḷ kuṉṟamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the lord, who sat as a man-lion</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the three worlds, others, and everything feared,</l>
<l>As [his] fury which raged reached [up] to scorch the heavens,</l>
<l>Is Lion-Man Mountain which is impossible to approach even a tiny bit,</l>
<l>There being, besides roaring fires and [craggy] rocks, hunters with bows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
